                    <span>Anyone like Krshna? This book, full of Sanskrit and Pali
terms, not only expands the mind with new vocabulary, but adds
a whole new dimension to the field of thought and understanding. If anyone wants a taste
  of Eastern Philosophy at its most difficult level, this is the book to read.</span>
                  
              
